colorTheme.name: colorTheme
colorTheme.sql: select doc.fullName, doc.title from XWikiDocument as doc, BaseObject as theme where doc.fullName=theme.name and (theme.className='ColorThemes.ColorThemeClass' or theme.className='FlamingoThemesCode.ThemeClass') and doc.fullName<>'ColorThemes.ColorThemeTemplate' and doc.fullName<>'FlamingoThemesCode.ThemeTemplate'

iconTheme.name: iconTheme
